Architecture

Overview

ai-treasury-agent is designed as an AI-powered treasury management system for crypto-native organizations, DAOs, protocols, and companies holding digital assets.

The system monitors wallets, consumes market data, evaluates portfolio risk, and prepares treasury recommendations through an AI decision layer.

The architecture is divided into five main components:

Wallets
Market Data
Risk Engine
Portfolio Manager
Execution Layer
